: ["paymentservice-2", "currencyservice-0", "cartservice-1", "shippingservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-06": ["emailservice-2", "productcatalogservice-0", "checkoutservice-2"], "aiops-k8s-07": ["emailservice-0", "currencyservice-2", "adservice-1", "frontend-1", "shippingservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-08": ["shippingservice-1", "redis-cart-0", "recommendationservice-0", "productcatalogservice-2", "paymentservice-0", "cartservice-2", "adservice-2"]}, "matched_anomaly": "A fault was detected from 2025-06-10T11:10:52Z to 2025-06-10T11:28:52Z. Please analyze its root cause.", "time_range": "2025-06-10 11:10:52+00:00 to 2025-06-10 11:28:52+00:00"}, "node_pod_mapping": {"aiops-k8s-01": ["checkoutservice-1", "emailservice-1", "recommendationservice-2", "shippingservice-0", "productcatalogservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-02": [], "aiops-k8s-03": ["shippingservice-2", "recommendationservice-1", "adservice-0", "paymentservice-1", "cartservice-0", "frontend-0"], "aiops-k8s-04": ["frontend-2", "currencyservice-1", "checkoutservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-05": ["paymentservice-2", "currencyservice-0", "cartservice-1", "shippingservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-06": ["emailservice-2", "productcatalogservice-0", "checkoutservice-2"], "aiops-k8s-07": ["emailservice-0", "currencyservice-2", "adservice-1", "frontend-1", "shippingservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-08": ["shippingservice-1", "redis-cart-0", "recommendationservice-0", "productcatalogservice-2", "paymentservice-0", "cartservice-2", "adservice-2"]}, "available_metric_names": ["client_error_ratio", "error_ratio", "io_util", "node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes", "rrt", "rrt_max"], "log_analysis_findings": "基于收集到的日志数据，我现在进行故障分析。从日志中可以看到明显的错误模式。\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\"gc\", \"DeadlineExceeded\", \"context deadline exceeded\", \"Byteman\", \"GCHelper\", \"InvocationTargetException\", \"Agent failed to start\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"adservice服务遭受gc故障注入，导致频繁垃圾回收，无法正常响应frontend的请求\",\n      \"evidence\": \"AdService--gc-1749553853 execute() 出现215次，frontend报错'failed to get ads: rpc error: code = DeadlineExceeded desc = context deadline exceeded'\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**分析总结**：\n1. **主要错误模式**：adservice服务被注入了GC故障（标签：`AdService--gc-1749553853`），导致频繁执行垃圾回收\n2. **影响范围**：所有3个adservice实例（adservice-0,1,2）都受到影响，出现大量GC相关日志\n3. **故障传播**：frontend服务无法从adservice获取广告数据，出现RPC超时错误（DeadlineExceeded）\n4. **关键证据**：Byteman故障注入框架的GCHelper类被用于触发GC，且Agent启动失败表明故障注入存在问题\n\n根因是adservice遭受了有意的GC故障注入，导致服务性能严重下降，无法响应前端请求。", "trace_analysis_findings": "基于收集到的链路追踪数据分析，我已经识别出故障时间段内的关键异常模式。以下是详细的分析结果：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"error_ratio\",\n    \"frontend->checkoutservice\",\n    \"checkoutservice->productcatalogservice\",\n    \"frontend->adservice\",\n    \"frontend->cartservice\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"PlaceOrder操作从正常143ms增加到异常257ms（延迟倍数1.8倍），且多个frontend节点调用checkoutservice均出现显著延迟\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\", \n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"GetProduct操作从正常14ms增加到异常27ms（延迟倍数1.9倍），作为checkoutservice的下游服务，其延迟影响了整个调用链\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"多个frontend节点调用AdService/GetAds出现'context deadline exceeded'错误（状态码4），错误率显著增加\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\", \n      \"evidence\": \"AddItem操作从正常3-5ms增加到异常27-29ms（延迟倍数5-8倍），是系统中延迟增加最显著的服务\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n## 关键发现总结：\n\n1. **延迟传播路径**：故障从下游服务向上传播：\n   - `productcatalogservice` → `checkoutservice` → `frontend`\n\n2. **最严重延迟**：`cartservice`的延迟增加最为显著（5-8倍），其次是`checkoutservice`（1.8倍）\n\n3. **错误模式**：`adservice`出现超时错误（context deadline exceeded），表明该服务可能无法及时响应请求\n\n4. **网络影响**：`recommendationservice`出现异常快速响应（从142ms降到9ms），可能是熔断或快速失败机制触发\n\n**根因推测**：`cartservice`和`productcatalogservice`的延迟增加是主要根因，导致上游`checkoutservice`和`frontend`级联延迟，同时`adservice`的错误进一步加剧了系统不稳定。", "metric_analysis_findings": "基于收集到的指标数据，我现在对故障进行分析。从数据中我发现了多个异常指标，主要涉及服务响应时间和节点内存可用性。\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"rrt_max\", \"rrt\", \"node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes\", \"io_util\", \"error_ratio\", \"client_error_ratio\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max指标显著下降（从43076.5降至3077.5，变化率173.33%），表明可能存在服务性能异常或配置问题\",\n      \"evidence\": \"adservice-1的rrt_max从正常中位数43076.5降至故障期中位数3077.5，变化率173.33%；rrt也从5994.96降至1680.46，变化率112.42%\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-03\",\n      \"reason\": \"node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes减少，表明节点内存资源紧张\",\n      \"evidence\": \"aiops-k8s-03节点的可用内存从正常中位数9353973760字节降至8502726656字节，减少9.53%\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max和error_ratio异常，表明服务性能下降且可能产生错误\",\n      \"evidence\": \"checkoutservice-0的rrt_max从240072增至303949，增加23.48%；error_ratio的p99值从0.29变为0.0，变化率200%\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"tidb-tikv\",\n      \"reason\": \"io_util的p99值异常，表明数据库IO利用率存在问题\",\n      \"evidence\": \"tidb-tikv的io_util p99值从0.21增至0.32，变化率41.51%\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**分析要点总结：**\n\n1. **主要问题**：多个服务的响应时间异常，特别是`rrt_max`指标显示adservice、paymentservice、emailservice等服务的最大响应时间出现显著变化。\n\n2. **节点级问题**：aiops-k8s-03节点内存可用性下降，可能影响部署在该节点上的服务（shippingservice-2、recommendationservice-1、adservice-0等）。\n\n3. **数据库问题**：TiDB-TiKV组件的IO利用率异常，可能影响依赖数据库的服务。\n\n4. **错误率异常**：checkoutservice-0的错误率指标显示异常变化模式。\n\n这些异常表明故障可能涉及多个组件，需要进一步分析服务间的依赖关系和时序相关性来确定根因。"}
